# _______________ QUESTIONS ___________________________________________________________________________

### Questions - GET - получить ВСЕ вопросы из БД.
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/questions/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Questions - POST - создать вопрос
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/questions/
Content-Type: application/json

# Варианты:
# user 1: Is AI a miracle?
# user 1: Is AI smart?
# user 1: The weather today is bad?
# user 2: Is the weather nice today?
# user 2: Do peonies bloom in your garden?
# user 2: Do you like the smell of peonies?
# user 2: Do you feel more alive in April than in winter?
# user 2: Do you usually take walks in May?

# user 1: Can AI ever truly understand human emotions?
# user 1: Do you trust AI to make decisions for you?

# user 3: Have you ever been at the Ocean shore?
# user 3: Do you think the ocean is wonderful?
# user 3: Have you ever traveled alone?
# user 3: Would you like to visit a place you’ve never heard of?
# user _: _

{
  "text": "Do you trust AI to make decisions for you?",
  "user_id": 1
}

### Questions - GET - получить вопрос по ID из БД. Ввести эндпоинт /1.
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/questions/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Questions - DELETE - УДАЛИТЬ вопрос по ID (вопрос 1) из БД. Ввести эндпоинт /1.
DELETE  http://127.0.0.1:5000/questions/14 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Questions - PUT - ИЗМЕНИТЬ вопрос по ID  (вопрос 1) из БД. Ввести эндпоинт /1.
PUT  http://127.0.0.1:5000/questions/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
     "text": "Is AI dangerous?"
}



