GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/responses/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Responses - POST - ОТПРАВИТЬ ответ на вопрос 1 в БД
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/responses/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

